The paper deals with channel estimation in massive multi-antenna systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The proposed method also utilizes random matrix theory, which is a topic related to statistical inference (cs.SI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with massive multi-antenna systems, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM).
